733
01:12:24,005 --> 01:12:25,836
My dress.

734
01:12:26,741 --> 01:12:28,208
What you've done.

735
01:12:28,376 --> 01:12:30,901
- Well, I buy you new dress.
- This is a new dress.

736
01:12:31,078 --> 01:12:32,272
I buy you hundred dresses.

737
01:12:32,446 --> 01:12:36,815
- This is the second time I've worn it. Look.
- Well, to hell with your dress.

738
01:12:37,351 --> 01:12:39,376
To hell with the dress. To hell with you.

739
01:12:39,554 --> 01:12:41,920
