757
01:14:37,071 --> 01:14:41,303
Don't be afraid. I have no intention
of shooting it out with you.

758
01:14:41,642 --> 01:14:43,940
Afraid, me?

759
01:14:44,111 --> 01:14:46,306
Where I come from,
we don't engage in dueling...

760
01:14:46,480 --> 01:14:49,415
...unless there's a point of honor involved.
- Honor?

761
01:14:49,583 --> 01:14:51,778
What about my honor?

762
01:14:51,952 --> 01:14:55,183
- I've often wondered.
- But I've just been violated.

763
01:14:55,356 --> 01:14:57,017
I struggled, he was just too strong.

764
01:14:57,191 --> 01:15:00,092
My dear wife, I may have been gagged,
but I wasn't blindfolded.

765
01:15:00,261 --> 01:15:03,196
- Well, what could I do?
- Nothing, I suppose, being what you are.

766
01:15:03,364 --> 01:15:07,095
- What do you mean, what I am?
- What you are and what you always will be.

767
01:15:07,268 --> 01:15:09,236
A slut, poor white trash.

768
01:15:09,403 --> 01:15:12,998
So that's the reward I get
for being faithful and true all these years.

769
01:15:13,174 --> 01:15:14,607
- Faith...?
- Poor white trash?

770
01:15:14,775 --> 01:15:16,265
Faithful?

771
01:15:16,444 --> 01:15:18,105
Do you think I'm a half-wit?

772
01:15:18,279 --> 01:15:21,510
All that flirting with everything in pants
that crossed our threshold.

773
01:15:21,682 --> 01:15:24,116
