to end up in the dark spots.

777
01:15:31,625 --> 01:15:33,559
- Whispering and giggling.
- Giggling?

778
01:15:33,728 --> 01:15:36,959
Yes, giggling, and kissing,
and hallelujahing in the honeysuckle.

779
01:15:37,131 --> 01:15:40,589
- Mr. Wakefield.
- Talk about Southern hospitality.

780
01:15:40,768 --> 01:15:44,260
Well, I've never been so insulted
in all my life.

781
01:15:44,438 --> 01:15:46,963
Oh, you can stop acting
the great lady now.

782
01:15:47,141 --> 01:15:48,574
I'm your husband, remember?

783
01:15:48,743 --> 01:15:51,075
I know where you come from
and what you are.

784
01:15:51,245 --> 01:15:54,737
I've tried all this time to hide it
from the world to preserve my good name.

785
01:15:54,915 --> 01:15:57,884
Good name,
that's all you ever think about.

786
01:15:58,052 --> 01:16:01,715
You and your pismire name.

787
01:16:02,256 --> 01:16:04,520
I should've thought about it
before I married you.

788
01:16:04,692 --> 01:16:07,661
You snob, you damn snob.

789
01:16:07,828 --> 01:16:11,195
<i>Silencio</i>, both of you.

790
01:16:11,365 --> 01:16:17,702
I don't like this big <i>argumento</i>.
It remind me of my mother and father.

791
01:16:19,340 --> 01:16:23,140
