of this thing, anyway?

792
01:16:23,310 --> 01:16:25,369
That breeze.

793
01:16:25,679 --> 01:16:28,944
Having nice quiet siesta.

794
01:16:29,116 --> 01:16:31,550
This stinking breeze.

795
01:16:33,320 --> 01:16:37,450
