You heard the things he said.

798
01:16:44,031 --> 01:16:46,522
How hateful he's being.
Our marriage is ruined.

799
01:16:46,700 --> 01:16:51,535
Señora, you cooked the pot of tamales,
I just pick up the lid.

800
01:16:51,705 --> 01:16:55,664
- Oh, please.
- And don't follow me.

801
01:16:55,843 --> 01:16:59,677
People follow me make me very <i>nervioso</i>.

802
01:17:01,448 --> 01:17:02,574
Let him go.

803
01:17:02,750 --> 01:17:06,015
Haven't you
cheapened yourself enough already?

804
01:17:19,500 --> 01:17:21,764
There she goes again.

805
01:17:22,803 --> 01:17:24,737
Always they do it.

806
01:17:24,905 --> 01:17:27,874
