832
01:18:52,026 --> 01:18:54,893
I've lived with you, slept with you.

833
01:18:55,062 --> 01:19:01,331
I've seen you shake all over in a cold sweat
and held your head while you vomited...

834
01:19:01,502 --> 01:19:04,266
...before you rode off to battle
with your horse prancing...

835
01:19:04,438 --> 01:19:06,963
...and the band playing Dixie.

836
01:19:07,141 --> 01:19:10,304
Yes, we both know
why you won't fight, don't we?

837
01:19:10,477 --> 01:19:14,004
You're a big, 14-karat coward.

838
01:19:14,181 --> 01:19:15,842
Coward, coward!

839
01:19:16,016 --> 01:19:18,075
CARRASCO: Enough.
- Who says so?

840
01:19:18,252 --> 01:19:19,583
Me, Carrasco.

841
01:19:19,753 --> 01:19:24,383
Oh, yes, the famous Carrasco.

842
01:19:24,558 --> 01:19:29,086
I've known about you for a long time.

843
01:19:29,263 --> 01:19:30,787
