854
01:20:08,202 --> 01:20:13,504
You're just a small tinhorn imitation
of yourself.

855
01:20:13,674 --> 01:20:16,370
A name without a body.

856
01:20:16,543 --> 01:20:18,135
A nothing.

857
01:20:18,312 --> 01:20:19,870
[SPITS]

858
01:20:25,686 --> 01:20:26,710
