880
01:24:04,071 --> 01:24:05,595
[GUN COCKS]

881
01:25:42,502 --> 01:25:45,801
Señor, please, <i>por favor</i>.

882
01:25:45,972 --> 01:25:47,303
Please...

883
01:25:49,910 --> 01:25:52,470
But you are gentleman, <i>coronel</i>.

884
01:25:57,484 --> 01:25:59,349
[GRO ANS]

885
01:26:20,774 --> 01:26:24,437
I tripped.

886
01:26:51,405 --> 01:26:54,067
You like to think people are big.

887
01:26:54,241 --> 01:26:58,405
Big heroes, big villains,
big something or other.

888
01:26:58,879 --> 01:27:01,677
