951
01:30:31,825 --> 01:30:33,850
- No.
- How much you get for it?

952
01:30:34,027 --> 01:30:35,995
Plenty, I bet.

953
01:30:36,162 --> 01:30:38,858
And you call me a coyote.

954
01:30:39,633 --> 01:30:42,158
You dumb ox, you.

955
01:30:44,471 --> 01:30:47,998
