960
01:31:06,960 --> 01:31:09,190
Coming this way.

961
01:31:09,863 --> 01:31:13,765
Oh, boy, this is one time
I ain't gonna ride the rods.

962
01:31:13,933 --> 01:31:17,300
Gotta get the damn thing to stop here.

963
01:31:18,471 --> 01:31:20,166
Eureka.

964
01:31:24,210 --> 01:31:25,973
Train's coming this way.

965
01:31:40,460 --> 01:31:43,429
